name: KEYNE - URCORNYVERSE
description: Development sketch for the character KEYNE, part of the new upcoming URCORNYVERSE experience launching 01.10.21. KEYNE loves to collect. They spend all their time in the URCORNYVERSE collecting collectible NFTs and uses them to make his nest. His nest is the biggest collection of NFTs in the URCORNYVERSE and is so big it had to be moved to the top of the tallest rainbow mountain in the URCORNYVERSE.
